Banckle,is,a,cloud,based,software,company,that,offers,businesses,with,online,customer,support,services,Banckle,Meeting,is,one,of,the,applications,available,through,Banckle,enabling,businesses,to,connect,with,their,customers,by,setting,up,meeting,room,on,the,cloud,The,Banckle,Meeting,API,lets,developers,to,personalize,their,customers,experience,by,integrating,it,with,their,applications,enabling,them,to,interact,with,customers,directly,from,the,application,The,API,allows,features,such,as,webinars,audio,and,video,conferences,and,more